03:44.160 --> 03:46.520
Milkman. Yes, I see.

03:46.640 --> 03:48.680
She is a bitch! A bitch!

03:48.760 --> 03:51.600
Yes, I hate her! I hate her!

03:51.840 --> 03:54.800
-[playing off-key]
-[all chanting] M-Dog. M-Dog.

03:56.760 --> 03:59.800
[chanting continues]

04:00.440 --> 04:03.360
Team M-Dog! Team M-Dog!

04:04.120 --> 04:05.640
