04:05.760 --> 04:07.640
Twist the bottle. Twist the bottle.

04:07.720 --> 04:10.680
Dad, stop being a pervert
or I'm throwing you out the van.

04:11.360 --> 04:12.400
Whose fault is that?

04:12.480 --> 04:14.680
Er, who wants to play
twist the bottle with my son?

04:15.000 --> 04:15.920
